=== libcyanid ===
A C++ wrapper library for injecting and capturing packets.The library is a
wrapper around the fantastic libnet and libpcap libraries. It aims to help the
development of shady software for C++ programmers that are not too found of
fooling around with C libraries that mess up their beautiful OO-design.

=== Requirements ===
- SCons
- libnet (1.1.x)
- libpcap

=== Build and install ===
Navigate to the cyanid directory and issue the following command to build
libcyanid:
$ scons

To install it, simply type:
$ sudo scons install


=== Examples ===
Sample code can be found in the examples subdirectory.
